      <h1>How to Negotiate Your Salary: The Psychology and Tactics That Get Results</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">Most people leave significant money on the table in salary negotiations. Learn the research-backed psychology and practical tactics that help you negotiate confidently and effectively.</p>
      <span>By <strong>{author}</strong></span>
    </header>

