        <li><a href="#anchoring">The Anchoring Effect in Salary Discussions</a></li>
        <li><a href="#batna">BATNA: Your Real Leverage</a></li>
        <li><a href="#framing">Framing and Timing Your Ask</a></li>
        <li><a href="#counter-offer">Counter-Offer Psychology</a></li>
